      • getObjectGraph

        public ObjectGraph getObjectGraph()
        Returns daggers object graph. As default Dagger1MvpLceViewStateActivity assumes that your Application implements Injector and that one will be accessed. If you want to do your own thing override this method. However, injecting should not be done in this method but in MosbyActivity.injectDependencies()
        Specified by:
        getObjectGraph in interface Injector
        See Also:
        MosbyActivity.injectDependencies()
